hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Could I order a new chequebook, please? www.safeway.com/greatgetaway Directed by Morgan Spurlock–of “Super Size Me” fame–the movie is something of a mirror to the scene that took place outside its premiere: screaming fans scrutinizing (and generally adoring) the every move of their favorite band members, trying to better know the guys. The band’s discography is made up of infectious, power-pop anthems professing love for girls who “don’t know they’re beautiful,” according to one hit, with a sexual innuendo thrown in here and there. The group has taken off.
